'''Frohard's Galactic Firearms''' was a small weapons manufacturing corporation. They were located on several [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core]] [[Planet/Legends|worlds]], including [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]] and [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. While they did produce standard blasters, they were known for the [[Magna Caster-100]] projectile weapon.<ref name="NEGWT">''[[The New Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref>

